![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/74eabe8d-face-4576-a5a9-3622727bcfee/16714.jpg)

The landscape of television royalty was redefined at the 77th Annual Primetime Emmy Awards. It was a night that solidified the reign of established hits while celebrating the arrival of new, unforgettable television.

From the major acting and directing categories to the creative arts, find out who else took home a prestigious trophy with the complete, official list of winners from television's biggest night below.

